unity - Target audience demographics - Pain points and needs - Market size and demand indicators - Competitive landscape - Unique value proposition 4. Product Ecosystem Overview - Core Book - Interactive Workbook - Web App (Balance Assessment Tool) - Digital Diary/Reminder System - Parent Stories Collection - Supporting content and courses 5. Core Framework: \"The Parent Identity Matrix\" - Relationship dimensions (self, partner, family, friends, coworkers, each child) - Balance assessment methodology - Framework for quantifying imbalance - Personalized action planning system 6. Content Architecture for Book - Chapter structure - Story integration points - Exercise placement - Reader journey map 7. Web App Development Roadmap - Feature specifications - User flow design - Technical requirements - Development phases - Integration with other products 8. Monetization Strategy Matrix - Revenue streams breakdown - Pricing models for each product - Upsell/cross-sell pathways - Subscription vs. one-time purchase analysis - Projected revenue scenarios 9. Tactical Implementation Plan Create detailed tables with columns: Phase, Action Step, Input Required, Expected Output, Timeline, Resources Needed, Success Metrics, Rationale/Data Phase 1: Research & Validation (Weeks 1-4) Phase 2: Framework Development (Weeks 5-8) Phase 3: Content Creation (Months 3-6) Phase 4: Product Development (Months 4-8) Phase 5: Marketing & Launch (Months 7-9) Phase 6: Growth & Optimization (Months 10-12) 10. Parent Stories Collection Strategy - Story sourcing methods - Interview framework - Editorial guidelines - Legal/permission requirements 11. Balance Assessment Tool Design - Scoring methodology - Question bank development - Algorithm for personalized recommendations - Visual dashboard mockup descriptions 12. Marketing & Launch Strategy - Pre-launch activities - Launch campaigns - Content marketing plan - Partnership opportunities - Community building tactics 13. Technical Stack Recommendations - 